text: Elian Memcaj (born 6 March 2002) is an Albanian professional basketball player who currently plays for KB Vllaznia in the Albanian Albanian Basketball League.BG Basket profileBIBL Profile He has also represented the Albania U18 national team.FIBA U18 profile ==References== Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:People from Shkodër County Category:People from Shkodër Category:Albanian men's basketball players Category:Basketball players from Shkodër Category:Sportspeople from Shkodër Category:Shooting guards
